high_descs: Walk to the end table by the sofa to the right.
Pick up the blue vase from the end table.
Walk to the floor lamp on the opposite side of the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Examine a blue vase by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn to your right, head towards the door then turn to your left
Pick up the blue vase on the small table
Walk across the room, past the sofa then turn to your right
anns.task_desc: Examine the vase by the light of the lamp

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the doorway, then turn left to face the small table.
Take the blue decorative glass off of the table.
Turn left and take a few steps forward, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn right.
anns.task_desc: To look at the decorative glass in the lighting.
